        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/e_chin/{size}/1388_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-12-23T02:24:30.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>William I never thought of <span class=\"hashtag\">#2</span> being done.  I assumed blending after fermentation, hmmm.  As to your use of the word concomitant\u2026 had to look that baby up.</p>",
