        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/arv_r/{size}/76949_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-12-23T04:43:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I thought d\u2019Arenberg down in Australia is doing this too with some bottling, maybe it was their Magpie bottling or something?  Presumably they did some research before doing this?</p>\n<p>======</p>\n<p>I\u2019m reading L-L original 1978 Rhone book right now, and its a blast seeing his opinions on the ancient vintages.  I realize its academic, since they\u2019re long gone and/or I would not buy them in any case, but is neat.</p>",
