        "created_at": "2016-12-23T05:28:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>What do you mean by fixing the color?  Being too dark in color considered a detriment somehow?  So if said winery were to co-ferment would that be a normal practice or done to enhance/mask due to vintage?</p>",
