        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Daniel Kim\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Daniel Kim:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It\u2019s pretty rare for producers in Hermitage to co-ferment. Can\u2019t think of anyone off the top of my head that does it intentionally.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Sorrel !</p>",
